title: JRE Review of 1286 with Anthony Jeselnik
description:
Anthony is one of my favorite comedians and his new stand up special does not disappoint. He's so well rehearsed that it inspires the shit out of me. His conversation with Joe is great and they talk all about how they got in to stand up and how fucking hard it is.

 

Enjoy my review folks!
